name: Giotto Teal
description: Fiore elevates the typical suit jacket with the Giotto. Subtle and stylish flourishes include light lines running down the left lapel and a strip of accent fabric along the arm seams that connect across the back of the jacket. The end result is an elegant and inspired addition to any wardrobe.
description_cn: 菲奥蕾的乔托外套让西装夹克设计上升到了新的高度。亮色线条沿翻领而下，一块亮色的布料横跨背部连接了两只袖子，风格含蓄又尽显时髦。最终的成品就是这件任何衣柜都不可或缺的精美外套。
